Daniel K. Frierson 
Executive Compensation
As Chief Executive Officer at DIXIE GROUP INC, Daniel K. Frierson  made $739,479 in total compensation.  Of this total $625,000 was received as a salary, $0 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $109,000 was awarded as stock and $5,479 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


